{"type":null,"faqId":37051,"title":"如何查看手环电量？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;color:red;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>查看电量有2种方式：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1、详细电量查看：通过APP查看，手环和手机通过蓝牙正常连接时，您可以在APP的设置界面中查看手环电量。这里电量可以显示百分比。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2、大概电量查看：直接点亮手环屏幕查看电量，屏幕上是没有数字百分比显示，只有格数大概的显示。（充电的时候才显示百分比）</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=121724\" style=\"width:2.2541666in;height:4.0111113in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span class=\"s1\">                </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=121725\" style=\"width:1.2222222in;height:1.78125in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2215","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1440750140000,"seriesProductName":"B2","visitedTimes":39,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"华为手环,B2,待机时间,使用时间,电量,低电量,低电量提醒","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}